Package org.Hardware.Motors.MotorControlModes

Record Class FeedforwardController

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
org.Hardware.Motors.MotorControlModes.FeedforwardController
Record Components:
kS - voltage to overcome static friction
kG - voltage to overcome gravity
kV - voltage to overcome friction or drag that reduces velocity
kA - voltage to overcome inertia or other resistive forces that reduce acceleration
public record FeedforwardController(double kS, double kG, double kV, double kA) extends Record
